data.description: Welcome Home To This Beautiful Spacious Raised Ranch. Amazing Curb Appeal As You Pull Up To This Oversized Expanded Driveway That Leads With The Front Door Opening Up To Open Floor Plan With Formal Living Room, Dining Room, Hardwood Floors Throughout And An Updated Kitchen With Granite Countertops. The Main Bathroom Is Designed With Modern Touches Throughout Cathedral Ceilings And A Solar Powered Skylight With Power Shade. Three Spacious Bedrooms Also On The First Floor. There Is So Much Possibility And Potential With The Den, Washer/Dryer Setup, Bedroom And Another Bath. Easy Access To The Front Yard Through The Two Car Garage, Backyard Is Fully Fenced With Privacy And Outdoor Living. Additional Features Include 200 Amp Service Installed 3 Years Ago, New Siding, New Burner Installed Nov 2023, Windows Installed 8 Years Ago, Appliances Under 5 Years And Chimney Has New Stainless Steel Liner, Cap & Repointed,   New Oil Tank, And Stainless Steel Hot Water Storage System.  Make This Your HOME.
